{"tid":2080770,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"一個月揸3000幾公里 計落條數想出架model 3","createTime":"2020-06-26T16:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T13:02:34.000Z","uid":746,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"f05e0d203d98d9873aa8ec7c6ff16b8463871949","tid":2080770,"uid":746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:10:03.000Z","msg":"想問下咁多位爸打<br />\n<br />\nModel 3 super change 要另外收費<br />\n但係公司個停車埸見到有佢個隻wall connector <br />\n想問吓呢啲使唔使錢？<br />\n<br />\n另外做功課先知啲充電站嘅收費好似好難搵<br />\n暫時淨係知道中電係唔使錢去到2020年底<br />\n想問吓有冇巴打知道唔使錢叉電嘅好地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7a122983f6351fa1feb27829dac5226b15cc8e","tid":2080770,"uid":771,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:12:35.000Z","msg":"如果油錢係你買車既concern <br />\n<br />\nmodel 3 慳唔到幾多<br />\n<br />\n保險貴勁多，差電都要幾毫1km<br />\n<br />\n慳唔到幾多，仲要成日on99 擺低架車差電<br />\n<br />\n屋企，公司冇差電位任擺一定唔買"},{"pid":"9f434aa745e40ddaa6c2c33b6c180ad1b9a074b1","tid":2080770,"uid":137335,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:15:13.000Z","msg":"買部油渣車渣算啦"},{"pid":"b39f16ba229589e3654d7b77f5f9716e7bc35217","tid":2080770,"uid":53285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:18:44.000Z","msg":"買diesel / hybrid"},{"pid":"465c2e7e4e02d95831286ae0e45c8993258a433a","tid":2080770,"uid":54023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:19:11.000Z","msg":"如果純粹想慳油錢唔睇牌子既話，出架p3 p4或者柴油好過<br />\n你model3維修又費，過多幾年想賣但粗咪又蝕車價，保險又貴，計返數可能仲貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006f00b8bf3a864f9dab800deff056c8fde7845f","tid":2080770,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:19:28.000Z","msg":"買架mazda 6 好過<br />\n柴油車入油平<br />\n起圍快，印象中有 40kgm ,勁過evo"},{"pid":"79c457b691f883691469e7fa832fc5faeed349f1","tid":2080770,"uid":82708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f05e0d203d98d9873aa8ec7c6ff16b8463871949","tid":2080770,"uid":746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:10:03.000Z","msg":"想問下咁多位爸打<br />\n<br />\nModel 3 super change 要另外收費<br />\n但係公司個停車埸見到有佢個隻wall connector <br />\n想問吓呢啲使唔使錢？<br />\n<br />\n另外做功課先知啲充電站嘅收費好似好難搵<br />\n暫時淨係知道中電係唔使錢去到2020年底<br />\n想問吓有冇巴打知道唔使錢叉電嘅好地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:46:30.000Z","msg":"wall connector係唔使錢<br />\n如果你返工有得差都ok 嘅<br />\n<br />\n我係另一個post 都POST過你可以睇下<br />\n電能車注意事項<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fzRivT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fzRivT</a>"},{"pid":"dffc81609b926ecc10bb17024d4f7bc35f573199","tid":2080770,"uid":82708,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:58:46.000Z","msg":"題外話 <br />\n渣得車就無得計慳錢<br />\n揸電動車慳到嘅係無嘢整 無乜手尾跟<br />\n叉電一定要計劃得好好 如果唔係 係真係成日都要去等位差電<br />\n<br />\n入油車有翻咁上下年份 <br />\n就會呢度爆 果度漏 最後開唔到"},{"pid":"dfae2e0deacdacf6f7775cb4ed93c8082e3de1f7","tid":2080770,"uid":75768,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>題外話 <br />\n渣得車就無得計慳錢<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">揸電動車慳到嘅係無嘢整 無乜手尾跟</span><br />\n叉電一定要計劃得好好 如果唔係 係真係成日都要去等位差電<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入油車有翻咁上下年份 <br />\n就會呢度爆 果度漏 最後開唔到</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n電子野會耐用過機械野真係第一次聽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw樓主揸電動車應該係唔錯既選擇，每個月行咁長里程我諗慳番黎既錢應該夠整車有凸"},{"pid":"055b5142d915f6198fae2e3c68b0ec9162defe76","tid":2080770,"uid":195125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T17:39:50.000Z","msg":"Model 3 出新車個保護包唔包整車？<br />\n<br />\n其實好多私人屋苑都有得安裝wall connector，如果泊一晚叉得夠第日嘅里數，以後連plan去油站入油嘅時間都慳返"},{"pid":"4ce633b68f5f868303d279de75ccf96ca49604d5","tid":2080770,"uid":177120,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"9f434aa745e40ddaa6c2c33b6c180ad1b9a074b1","ti